-- Massmart May Accept Conditions on Wal-Mart Takeover, Business Day Reports
-- B y   P a u l   R i c h a r d s o n
-- 2010-11-29T05:27:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-29/massmart-may-accept-conditions-on-wal-mart-takeover-business-day-reports.html
Massmart Holdings Ltd. may accept
conditions sought by labor unions to secure a proposed takeover
by Wal-Mart Stores Inc., Business Day reported, citing Llewellyn
Steeneveldt, the executive head of legal affairs at the South
African retailer.  Conditions may include a moratorium on retrenchments for a
period after the takeover is completed, the Johannesburg-based
newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  